channel.title: Faded Scape 718/742
channel.description:
[CENTER]Faded Scape is a newer economy server with a unique and advanced 718 source loading a wonderful 742 cache. We've taken to the time to add quite a few custom items, Such as a Black Santahat, Black H'Ween, White H'Ween, Drygores, Seasingers, Deathlotus, And much, much more. Our server is hosted on a VPS with 2 GB of RAM for the best performance for our player count. Our server doesn't beg you for donations although donations do pay for the server we can last a good 4 or 5 months without a single donation because we've saved up and have a backup paypal with the funds required for our server bills. As of right now we do not have a full staff team, And we do need active and time giving players to be staff
